Class GroupClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • Client
      • GroupClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientInterface, GroupInterface

    public class GroupClient
extends Client
implements GroupInterface, ClientInterface
    Handles connections to the GroupServer. Note however that the GroupClient does not know who it is connecting to, but will assume that the server understands the protocol.
